  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Scientific initiation for 120 students in Paraguay</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is aimed towards developing key skills in young talents from Paraguay through challenging mathematics classes designed to emphasize logical reasoning and the scientific method. The program focuses on students between 12 and 18 years old, predominantly from low-income families and with diminished academic opportunities. The project intends to provide improved chances of accessing to superior education for these young and it&apos;s the first and only one with these features in Paraguay.</narrative>
  </description>
